+Quick Start / Overview
+======================
+- Build the ARM Trusted Firmware binary (see "ARM Trusted firmware (ATF)" below)
+- Build U-Boot (see "SPL/U-Boot" below)
+- Transfer to an uSD card (see "microSD card" below)
